            <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 11:00:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[acer]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Predator League]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[宏碁]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1215471</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由 Acer 主辦的亞太區 Predator  League 2024 總決賽 1 月 14 日於菲律賓馬尼拉圓滿落幕，亞洲 26 隊參賽精鋭團體分別來自香港、日本、韓國、泰國等地，以《DOTA2》、《VALORANT》兩款遊戲角逐冠軍，最終 2 款遊戲「Predator Shield」掠奪者盾牌冠軍寶座皆由主辦國菲律賓包辦。據悉 2025 年初將轉戰馬來西亞，勢必再掀精彩決賽戰局。</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8779 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855533?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
職業電競隊伍 Oblivion Force 代表香港出征《Valorant》比賽，成功於分組賽事擊敗台灣代表 RNKKO Esports，可惜仍無緣晉身決賽。是次 Predator  League 2024 比賽《Dota2》及《Valorant》冠軍隊伍均來自東道主菲律賓，分別為「Team Secret 」及 「Blacklist International 」。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1215944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240118181953-694x157.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="157" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240118181953-694x157.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240118181953.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港代表隊 Oblivion Force 以 1:0 戰勝台灣代表隊 RNKKO Esports<br />
圖片來源：<a href="https://www.thespike.gg/match/oblivion-force-rnkko-esports/112333">The Spike</a></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8741 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855667?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲介紹香港代表隊 Oblivion Force 出場時刻<br />
得獎參賽隊伍訊息如下：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1216269 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240121124855-694x358.png" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240121124855-694x358.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240121124855.png 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>各隊伍台上領獎情況:</h2><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9015" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856056?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9010" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856116?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9011" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856163?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9021" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904856030?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9043" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904857628?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲完美落幕</p><h2>全場滿座有明星歌唱表演</h2><p>除了現場精彩的 Predator League 電競比賽，Acer 亦邀請了不少偶像團體到場。開幕日有男團 SB 19 成員 Felip 及當地知名女歌手 Ylona Garcia，兩人精彩的表演將本來激烈的氣氛帶至最高點。其後邀請了 Acer 品牌大使 Sarah Geronimo 與 SB19 同台共演；閉幕典禮則邀請了女歌手 KZ Tandingan 與馬尼拉交響樂團合奏，讓活動完美落幕。</p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8737" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855443?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_9045" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904857659?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/15/acer-ces-2024/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】Acer 推出全新電競筆電系列　同場加映旗艦顯示卡和曲面螢幕</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/hornington-outlet/shop_guide/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">漢科聖誕開倉　精選電競螢幕、手掣、鍵盤掃貨好時機</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>轉換品牌形象</h2><p>Acer 泛亞營運總部總經理侯知遠表示，「2024 亞太區 Predator League 總決賽精彩落幕，不只展現電競社羣的蓬勃發展，也顯示 Predator 產品支援玩家們需求的決心。」</p><p>侯知遠又指，今年 Acer 會轉換品牌形象，採取更加積極的策略，轉為以生活方式主導吸引客人購買 Acer 產品。Acer 會在智能生活產品、AI 解決方案及維修服務方面投放更多資源，為用家提供更優良體驗，以吸引更多年輕人留意 Acer 品牌。</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8785" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855593?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲會場設有遊戲試玩及 acer 產品體驗</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8788 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855831?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲會場攤位遊戲</p><h2>Acer 空清日本成績爆燈</h2><p>除了電競、電腦方面的產品外，Acer 亦積極開拓產品線。早前推出的 Acerpure 系列空氣清新機亦取得極大成功，營收增長率在日本錄得 2670%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1215948" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/415666473_1511160686-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/415666473_1511160686-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/415666473_1511160686.jpg 1202w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br />
&nbsp;</p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8901 2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904858003?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>下屆 2025 年前進馬來西亞</h2><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8724" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/904855738?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/15/acer-ces-2024/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】Acer 推出全新電競筆電系列　同場加映旗艦顯示卡和曲面螢幕</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/hornington-outlet/shop_guide/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">漢科聖誕開倉　精選電競螢幕、手掣、鍵盤掃貨好時機</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/20/predator-league-2024/game-channel/">2024 亞太區 Predator League 菲國精彩落幕，東道主包辦 2 冠</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
